<%# [MG-05] NIS 72-Hour Notification Clock
    Countdown widget shows "Next Event:" + mm:ss for soonest pending timer.
    When timer fires (delayMs elapsed), `setGlobal` executes and markFired() removes from countdown.
    Urgent alerts: < 5min = amber, < 1min = red with pulse animation.

    NIS Regulations 2018: OES operators in the electricity sector must notify NCSC within 72 hours
    of becoming aware of an incident with significant impact. Incident awareness: 06:28.
    Game-time compression: 45 min = 2700000ms (same as ICO timer in sis01_healthcare).
    Consequence: Priya fires a bark and switches to nis_deadline_consequence knot in npc_priya_chandra.ink. %>
    {
      "id": "nis_deadline",
      "label": "NIS 72-Hour Notification Deadline",
      "delayMs": 2700000,
      "condition": "!globalVars.ncsc_notified",
      "setGlobal": { "nis_deadline_missed": true },
      "showCountdown": true,
      "onceOnly": true
    },
<%# [MG-04] Hydrogen Gas Alarm Progression — ENG-02 timed escalation
    Both timers start when anomaly_detected=true and are cancelled on esd_activated=true.
    T+22m (1320000ms): hydrogen advisory — sets hydrogen_alarm=true, Priya eventMapping fires radio message.
    T+40m (2400000ms): evacuation — sets facility_evacuated=true if ESD still not pressed.
    delayMs are real-time milliseconds (game-time; players have ~70min total session).
    Physical: evacuation tone via audio relay is a separate PHYS task — not implemented here. %>
    {
      "id": "h2_advisory",
      "label": "H₂ Advisory — T+22m",
      "startOnGlobal": "anomaly_detected",
      "delayMs": 1320000,
      "cancelOnGlobal": "esd_activated",
      "setGlobal": { "hydrogen_alarm": true },
      "showCountdown": false,
      "onceOnly": true
    },
    {
      "id": "h2_evacuation",
      "label": "H₂ Evacuation — T+40m",
      "startOnGlobal": "anomaly_detected",
      "delayMs": 2400000,
      "cancelOnGlobal": "esd_activated",
      "condition": "!globalVars.esd_activated",
      "setGlobal": { "facility_evacuated": true },
      "showCountdown": false,
      "onceOnly": true
    }
